{"tid":384329,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長毛籲籌款助劉小麗上訴","createTime":"2017-09-02T08:19:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T09:34:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7aca5269cc94c859325f9a70ec99fd06aeb794d1","tid":384329,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:19:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20140209&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170902\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20140209%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170902&d=RYzsNvr9Civu4n4MXYouBpzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=0bd0b3a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20140209%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170902&h=5c5570ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20140209&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170902</a><br />\n<br />\n長毛籲籌款助劉小麗上訴<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170902/large/a02b01a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170902%2Flarge%2Fa02b01a.gif&h=8711978c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁國雄（左）指早前曾與劉小麗（右）商討上訴事宜。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】社民連「長毛」梁國雄昨日現身灣仔街站時，狠批本港法庭承認人大釋法有追溯力的有關決定，「𠵱家個問題係，等於一班老人家喺北京亂掟垃圾、掟屎後，要香港啲大法官幫手去抹、去執返，結果（香港大法官）搞到自己一身都係」。<br />\n<br />\n已經成功申請法援、就取消議員資格案件提出上訴的「長毛」梁國雄預告，將會在本月11日之前提交上訴狀，並且透露早前曾經與目前仍然未決定是否上訴的劉小麗商討，「我相信香港巿民會籌到足夠嘅錢畀佢（劉小麗）上訴，希望佢返香港之後，大家可以令到佢有信心」。<br />\n<br />\n倡民主派議員捐薪酬<br />\n<br />\n梁國雄又建議，每名現任民主派立法會議員，每人捐出一個月的議員薪酬，支持被取消資格的民主派議員提出上訴，更加希望香港巿民能夠更大力捐款支持「守護公義基金」。梁國雄坦言：「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果九龍西議席打孖一齊選，建制派即可以渾水摸魚攞返一席。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n目前身在海外、仍然在考慮是否就議員資格被取消一案提出上訴的劉小麗，昨日回覆本報電話查詢時指出，自己目前最大的考慮，是可能屬於天文數字的訟費問題。<br />\n劉小麗表示，明日回來香港之後，將會再與律師團隊以及民主派開會討論，然後再決定是否提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n■記者林俊謙"},{"pid":"b8bd42ef450f6be49c269f955165f359f7325063","tid":384329,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:43:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4fe8d9a20b3596c95aeeaf3e470892509b972339","tid":384329,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:43:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4058a4c8f9b988bec24503b04ea1dd5e71672f7","tid":384329,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:46:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>o岩啦,我不嬲都話叫連登仔夾錢比佢打官司<br />\n連登仔平時又反共建國又盛,唔係依加縮啊?</blockquote><br />\n射落海好過"},{"pid":"bdd80c9af8f5f66c0aa326def39526b47c6ec78a","tid":384329,"uid":133641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:46:51.000Z","msg":"第一個回覆已經係五毛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d7b76b23c2bbd88d6e4a5de5f14d9048cadb93","tid":384329,"uid":54183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:49:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f4c714a3ff6e22447f59cf8643204a934d6225e","tid":384329,"uid":37776,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T09:20:43.000Z","msg":"做咩要夾錢俾個有兩層樓( 一層係自住）既小麗上訴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b4fecfd5470200c58af5d9de3790b8e3923c16","tid":384329,"uid":71315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T09:32:07.000Z","msg":"小麗老母"},{"pid":"65c10b2b9f4e0d4adc1ab30de952cbc2e1952f02","tid":384329,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T09:56:13.000Z","msg":"出泥做G啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想屌"},{"pid":"cc184e70427795d676e10e084a2796c0dee98e7e","tid":384329,"uid":71315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl